    {
      "id": "github-repo-home-node-contract-template",
      "type": "markdown",
      "label": "Home-Page Template Contract",
      "position": {
        "x": 1360,
        "y": 1040
      },
      "width": 420,
      "height": 340,
      "visible": true,
      "showLabel": true,
      "data": {
        "markdown": "# Home-Page Template Contract\n\nThe home-page template should scaffold a destination-centered landing graph.\n\nPrimary job:\n- tell a visitor what this place is\n- show the main destinations\n- make the first click obvious\n\nMinimum structure:\n- declaration\n- title\n- type-definition\n- one `port` node bound to the `ui-view` class\n- at least two primary destination ports\n- one short supporting-context node\n\nRecommended composition zones:\n- Identity\n- Primary Destinations\n- Supporting Context\n- Secondary Destinations (optional)\n\nRules:\n- page-first, not document-first\n- destination-centered, not article-centered\n- hero plus destinations before explanation\n- use existing primitives where possible\n- do not make repo-specific assumptions\n\nDefault surface:\n- a `port` node bound to the `ui-view` class should be the main public surface\n\nWhat success looks like:\n- a reader can answer “what is this place?”\n- a reader can identify the main next click immediately\n- the graph still works for repo homes, product homes, section homes, and workspace homes.",
        "isRoot": false,
        "root": false,
        "_classBinding": {
          "key": "markdown",
          "sourceRef": "github://twilite-zone/public/library/classes/nodes/markdown.node-class.node",
