    {
      "id": "github-repo-home-node-contract-resolution",
      "type": "markdown",
      "label": "Repo / Home Resolution Contract",
      "position": {
        "x": 1880,
        "y": 1040
      },
      "width": 420,
      "height": 340,
      "visible": true,
      "showLabel": true,
      "data": {
        "markdown": "# Repo / Home Resolution Contract\n\nPreferred rule:\n- home resolution is declaration-driven\n\nBootstrap fallback:\n- if no landing surface is declared, resolve `/root.node`\n\nWhy:\n- declaration keeps publishing intentional\n- fallback keeps setup simple\n- the model supports richer repo shapes later without breaking bootstrap\n\nImplementation note:\nConvention should be the default path, not the source of truth, once a repo declares a stronger landing surface.",
        "isRoot": false,
        "root": false,
        "_classBinding": {
          "key": "markdown",
          "sourceRef": "github://twilite-zone/public/library/classes/nodes/markdown.node-class.node",
