    {
      "id": "github-repo-home-node-contract-repo-template",
      "type": "markdown",
      "label": "Repo-Home Template Contract",
      "root": false,
      "position": {
        "x": 2400,
        "y": 1400
      },
      "width": 460,
      "height": 380,
      "visible": true,
      "showLabel": true,
      "data": {
        "markdown": "# Repo-Home Template Contract\n\nThe repo-home template specializes the generic home-page template for a GitHub repository as the main public-facing landing surface.\n\nPrimary job:\n- identify the repository clearly\n- show what this repo is for\n- make the first public destination obvious\n- expose the key repo destinations without turning into a long article\n\nMinimum structure:\n- declaration\n- title\n- type-definition\n- one `port` node bound to the `ui-view` class\n- one `github-repo` node\n- one featured/primary destination\n- at least one additional repo destination\n- one short repo-context/supporting node\n\nRecommended composition zones:\n- Repo Identity\n- Featured Start Here\n- Key Destinations\n- Repo Context\n- Supporting Links (optional)\n\nRules:\n- specialize the generic home-page template, do not replace it\n- the `github-repo` node owns repo identity and repo-home semantics\n- the page owns composition and public orientation\n- destination-first, with explanation kept short\n- no GitHub installation/write-status UI on the home page by default\n\nDefault surface:\n- a `port` node bound to the `ui-view` class should be the main public repo-home surface\n\nWhat success looks like:\n- a visitor can answer “what repo is this?” immediately\n- a visitor can tell where to start\n- the page reads as a public repo landing surface, not as an internal planning graph\n- the template still works for public repos beyond Twilite itself.",
        "definitionKey": "markdown",
        "_classBinding": {
          "key": "markdown",
          "sourceRef": "github://twilite-zone/public/library/classes/nodes/markdown.node-class.node",
          "ref": "github://twilite-zone/public/library/classes/nodes/markdown.node-class.node"
        },
        "_bridge": {
          "classKey": "markdown",
          "classRef": "github://twilite-zone/public/library/classes/nodes/markdown.node-class.node"
        }
      }
    },
